description: Unit testing file for the Schedule model in a kindergarten management system's frontend project. Contains test cases for Schedule class instantiation, methods, and behaviors.

classes.name: Schedule
classes.description: Data model representing a schedule entry for a class, including properties like id, className, subject, startTime, endTime, dayOfWeek, teacherId, room, description, and isActive. Also includes methods for creating time ranges and mapping to/from JSON.

methods.name: timeRange
methods.description: Returns a formatted string representing the start and end time of the schedule.

methods.name: toMap
methods.description: Converts the Schedule instance into a Map suitable for serialization.

methods.name: fromMap
methods.description: Creates a Schedule instance from a Map, typically deserialized JSON.

methods.name: copyWith
methods.description: Creates a copy of the Schedule instance with optional modified fields.
